  <name>AnalogStudio</name>
  <summary>Professional Analog Circuit Design Tool</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      AnalogStudio is a professional-grade EDA (Electronic Design Automation) tool for designing, simulating, 
      and analyzing analog circuits. Built by Algo Science Lab, it provides comprehensive features for circuit 
      design engineers and hobbyists.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Intuitive schematic capture with comprehensive component library</li>
      <li>SPICE-based circuit simulation using ngspice</li>
      <li>Advanced waveform analysis and visualization</li>
      <li>Layout editor for PCB design</li>
      <li>Custom symbol and component creation</li>
      <li>Design rule checking (DRC) engine</li>
      <li>Support for multiple file formats (.asch, .alib, .asproj, .sy)</li>
      <li>Professional-grade documentation and help system</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

